Package: crunchtabs
Type: Package
Title: Report (Toplines and Banners) Generation for Crunch Datasets
Description: This package provides functions for report generation:
    - Toplines (one-way frequency tables),
    - Banners (cross tabulations).
Version: 0.4.0
